# Date And Time Usage

- Use `date-fns` for date parsing, formatting, arithmetic, and comparisons.
- Use `date-fns-tz` when code needs explicit timezone conversion.
- Do not introduce `Intl.DateTimeFormat` or hand-rolled timezone math for app date/time behavior.
- Keep date/time helpers in nearby utility files when they are used by components.
